data.name: rbMarketDefault_NotSend.ToolTip
data.value: "Quick Decision Checkbox" is OFF by default. To send market data from single stations check the "Quick Decision Checkbox". After sending the Checkbox will be unchecked again. No more data will be send - until you recheck the "Quick Decision Checkbox".

data.name: rbMarketDefault_Send.ToolTip
data.value: "Quick Decision Checkbox" is ON by default. To avoid sending of market data from single stations uncheck the "Quick Decision Checkbox". After sending the Checkbox is checked again. Next time data will be send again - until you uncheck the "Quick Decision Checkbox" again.

data.name: label2.ToolTip
data.value: If a sender is registered here, it's data never will be rejected due to implausible values. Use it with non-OCR interfaces (interfaces with Companion API). "Add" or select row and "Delete" to change.
